Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.58,0:00:06.83,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,昴君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.83,0:00:09.85,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,噢 雷姆 你居然申请参加了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.85,0:00:11.83,Default,Rem,0000,0000,0000,,请拿一本看看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.83,0:00:13.99,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,居然这么熟练
